<h5 id="subject_1109749">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=df790cd498609ebff7a37cd20d1664bf&amp;topic=124794.msg1109749#msg1109749" rel="nofollow">【Reddit】让你不会在第六纪里像个傻逼一样死掉的规则</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1109749'));undefined;">繁</a>
